Package: botscan
Type: Package
Title: Scans Twitter Conversations For Bots
Version: 2.1.0
Author: Kurt Wirth and Ryan T. Moore
Maintainer: Kurt Wirth <KurtAWirth@gmail.com>
Description: This package accepts any Twitter search query as an input and
    outputs the percentage of the conversation's tweets that are
    predicted to be authored by non-humans, or "bots". This tool uses rtweets 
    to search Twitter and botometer and its machine learning technique to 
    analyze handles.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    reticulate,
    rtweet
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: testthat
